Â  ## ğŸš° Staking, delegation and rewards
Â  ### Withdraw all rewards
Â  'empowerd tx distribution withdraw-all-rewards --from $wallet --chain-id circulus-1 --gas auto --gas-adjustment 1.3'
Â  ### Withdraw commission
Â  'empowerd tx distribution withdraw-rewards $EMPOWER_VALOPER_ADDRESS --from $wallet --commission --fees 200umpwr'
Â  ### Delegate Stake
Â  'empowerd tx staking delegate $EMPOWER_VALOPER_ADDRESS 10000000utia --from $wallet --chain-id circulus-1 --gas=auto --gas-adjustment 1.3'
